  <h2 id="tips">🔥 Tips Menang Mega888 (Strategy 2026)</h2>
  <p>Ramai player tanya, ada tak "Scanner Mega888"? Jawapannya: <strong>TIADA</strong>. System Mega888 guna RNG (Random Number Generator). Kalau ada orang jual scanner APK, itu scammer. Tapi, otai-otai ada cara main (Play Smart):</p>

  <h4>1. Jangan Main Masa "Maintenance"</h4>
  <p>Biasanya hari Khamis pagi (10am - 1pm), server akan buat maintenance. Masa ni RTP reset. Kalau masuk time ni, memang "sedut". Tunggu server stable dulu baru masuk.</p>

  <h4>2. Teknik "Main Tahan" (Bankroll Management)</h4>
  <p>Jangan terus bet besar (RM5 - RM20) kalau baru login. Start dengan bet kecik (RM0.50) untuk "panaskan" ID. Bila nampak scatter makin kerap keluar, baru naikkan bet. Kalau game tu asyik telan kredit, <strong>tukar game lain</strong>. Jangan paksa.</p>

  <h4>3. Cuci Kerap (Withdraw Strategy)</h4>
  <p>Pantang larang utama: Jangan tamak. Kalau modal RM50 dah naik RM300, <strong>CUCI TERUS</strong>. Jangan simpan baki. Keluar dulu, rehat sejam, baru masuk balik.</p>

  <h2>📖 Mega888 Dictionary (Glossary)</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cuci (Wash):</strong> The act of withdrawing your winnings. E.g., "Boss, nak cuci RM500."</li>
    <li><strong>Topup / Masuk:</strong> Depositing money into your game ID. Minimum deposit is usually RM20.</li>
    <li><strong>Free Spin / Scatter:</strong> A bonus round where you spin without using credit.</li>
    <li><strong>RTP (Return To Player):</strong> The percentage of money the game pays back.</li>
    <li><strong>Angpao:</strong> Random bonus credit dropped by the system during special events.</li>
  </ul>
